<plot>Plainclothes Police Inspector, Ravi, has been assigned the task of apprehending notorious gangster, Shera, who, however, proves to be too elusive for him. Ravi then seeks the assistance of another gangster, who is doing time in prison, by the name of Raja. Ravi goes to meet Raja in prison, and requests his co-operation. Raja readily agrees to assist Ravi in this matter, and he is released from prison, in the custody of Ravi. What Ravi does not know that Raja has his own agenda behind this so-called co-operation, and will not hesitate to exploit his new-found freedom to the maximum possible level.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?039215</url></doc>
